'''Gjerstad''' is a village in [[Osterøy]] municipality in [[Hordaland]] county, [[Norway]].  The village is located in the central part of the island of [[Osterøy (island)|Osterøy]], just north of the village of [[Austbygdi, Osterøy|Austbygdi]].  The municipal centre of [[Lonevåg]] lies about {{convert|4|km}} north of Gjerstad.  [[Gjerstad Church (Osterøy)|Gjerstad Church]] is located in this village, serving the central part of the island.

